  "summary": "Moderate: java-11-openjdk security and bug fix update",
  "details": "The java-11-openjdk packages provide the OpenJDK 11 Java Runtime Environment and the OpenJDK 11 Java Software Development Kit.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\n* OpenJDK: handshake DoS attack against DTLS connections (JSSE, 8287411) (CVE-2023-21835)\n* OpenJDK: soundbank URL remote loading (Sound, 8293742) (CVE-2023-21843)\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n\nBug Fix(es):\n\n* Prepare for the next quarterly OpenJDK upstream release (2023-01, 11.0.18) [almalinux-8] (BZ#2157797)",
